                <h1>Too gay or not gay enough?</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/c8fd5860-655c-49d8-8083-344c4174b089.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="Image&#x20;Courtesy&#x20;of&#x20;Wikimedia&#x20;Commons" class="w-100">
